## MapViewOptions.customAntialiasSettings property

Antialias settings for the map rendering. It is better to disable the native antialising if the custom antialiasing is enabled.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
customAntialiasSettings?: IMapAntialiasSettings;
```
